Sentence: A few years later, George Greggson and Jean Morrel attend a party held by Rupert Boyce, an amateur scholar of the paranormal
While there, George and Jean run into Rashaverak, an Overlord making use of Boyce's research library
This fainting fit worries George, and he (George) proposes marriage to Jean
Back on Earth, George and Jean begin their life together
George and Jean take their two kids, Jeffrey and Jennifer, with them
Jean and George die as New Athens blows itself up in a nuclear explosion
